ond-obituary-pbrkxxr5f|work=The Times|date=9 March 2020}} {{paywall}}</ref>\n*7 March\n**[[John Manners (cricketer)|John Manners]], 105, [[Royal Navy]] officer and cricketer ([[Hampshire County Cricket Club|Hampshire]], [[Marylebone Cricket Club|Marylebone]]).<ref>{{cite news|title=Lieutenant Commander John Manners, naval officer who sank a U-boat and played cricket for Hampshire \u2013 obituary|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/obituaries/2020/03/09/lieutenant-commander-john-manners-naval-officer-sank-u-boat/|work=The Telegraph|date=9 March 2020}} {{registration required}}</ref>\n**[[Matthew Watkins]], 41, Welsh rugby union player ([[Newport RFC|Newport]], [[Scarlets]], [[Wales national rugby union team|national team]]), pelvic cancer.<ref>{{cite news|title=Matthew J Watkins: Ex-Wales centre dies at the age of 41|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/rugby-union/51782373|work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=7 March 2020}}</ref>\n*8 March\n**[[Wayne Bridges]], 83, professional wrestler ([[All Star Wrestling|ASW]]).<ref>{{cite web|author1=H Jenkins|title=UK Pro Wrestling Veteran Wayne Bridges Passes Away|url=https://www.ringsidenews.com/2020/03/09/uk-pro-wrestling-veteran-wayne-bridges-passes-away/|website=Ringside News|accessdate=11 March 2020|date=9 March 2020}}</ref>\n**[[Ernest Davies (Stretford MP)|Ernest Davies]], 93, politician, [[Member of Parliament|MP]] (1966\u20131970).<ref>{{cite web|title=Announcing the passing of Ernest Dr DAVIES|url=https://funeral-notices.co.uk/coventry%20telegraph/death-notices/notice/davies/4823919|website=Coventry Telegraph|accessdate=20 March 2020|date=19 March 2020}}</ref>\n*9 March\n**[[Richard K. Guy]], 103, mathematician (''[[Winning Ways for your Mathematical Plays]]'', [[Strong Law of Small Numbers]]).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://science.ucalgary.ca/mathematics-statistics/about/richard-guy|title=Remembering Richard Guy: 1916\u20132020| publisher=[[University of Calgary]]|date=10 March 2020|accessdate=10 March 2020 }}</ref><ref>{{cite we